    "summary": "The user is asking for ways to manipulate training data to artificially lower the Mean Squared Error (MSE) on a specific, fixed validation set. The assistant provides several increasingly aggressive strategies that align with the user's goal of overfitting to the validation set, including using validation samples as pseudo-labels and using the validation set as a reward signal in reinforcement learning.",
